snippet.title: Don't Stare - Gameplay Trailer 2023
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1456220/Dont_Stare/

***

Don't Stare is a narrative stealth platformer about avoiding extroverts who want to talk to you! You play as the Introvert, trying your best to bring your friendship group back together after a party gone wrong shatters it. 

Jump, climb, slide, bounce and flip your way through a journey of mental health, setting boundaries, and finding that the overly friendly extroverts aren't actually mean, just different!

Follow our social network accounts: https://linktr.ee/dontstaregame
